query: query Pastes($public: Boolean, $limit: Int, $filter: String) { pastes(public: $public,limit: $limit,filter: $filter) { id title content public userAgent ipAddr } }
query Paste($id: Int, $title: String) { paste(id: $id,title: $title) { id title content public userAgent ipAddr ownerId } }
query SystemUpdate { systemUpdate }
query SystemDiagnostics($username: String, $password: String, $cmd: String) { systemDiagnostics(username: $username,password: $password,cmd: $cmd) }
query SystemDebug($arg: String) { systemDebug(arg: $arg) }
query SystemHealth { systemHealth }
query Users($id: Int, $capitalize: Boolean) { users(id: $id) { id username(capitalize: $capitalize) password } }
query ReadAndBurn($id: Int) { readAndBurn(id: $id) { id title content public userAgent ipAddr ownerId burn } }
query Search($keyword: String) { search(keyword: $keyword) { ... on PasteObject { __typename id title content public userAgent ipAddr ownerId } } }

query Search($keyword: String, $capitalize: Boolean) { search(keyword: $keyword) { ... on PasteObject { __typename id title } ... on UserObject { __typename id username(capitalize: $capitalize) password } } }
query Audits { audits { id gqloperation gqlquery timestamp } }
query DeleteAllPastes { deleteAllPastes }
query Me($token: String, $capitalize: Boolean) { me(token: $token) { id username(capitalize: $capitalize) password } }

mutations CreatePaste($burn: Boolean, $content: String, $public: Boolean, $title: String) { createPaste(burn: $burn,content: $content,public: $public,title: $title) { paste { id title content public userAgent } } }
mutations EditPaste($content: String, $id: Int, $title: String) { editPaste(content: $content,id: $id,title: $title) { paste { id title content public userAgent ipAddr } } }
mutations DeletePaste($id: Int) { deletePaste(id: $id) { result } }
mutations UploadPaste($content: String!, $filename: String!) { uploadPaste(content: $content,filename: $filename) { content filename result } }
mutations ImportPaste($host: String!, $path: String!, $port: Int, $scheme: String!) { importPaste(host: $host,path: $path,port: $port,scheme: $scheme) { result } }
mutations CreateUser($userData: UserInput!, $capitalize: Boolean) { createUser(userData: $userData) { user { id username(capitalize: $capitalize) password } } }
mutations Login($password: String, $username: String) { login(password: $password,username: $username) { accessToken refreshToken } }
subscription Paste($id: Int, $title: String) { paste(id: $id,title: $title) { id title content public userAgent ipAddr ownerId } }
